overview.en: GC,Chinese Name: Jinbi, token: GC2019, total 10 billion. One is based on ERC-20, only used as BoChat social platform points, It’s can be converted into products or rights. Become a BoChat user or invite your friends to receive a gold coin points award.
overview.zh: GC,中文名称：金币，令牌：GC2019，总量100亿枚。一款基于ERC-20标准积分，仅作为BoChat社交平台积分使用，可以兑换产品或权益。成为BoChat用户或邀请您好友获得金币积分奖励。
